name: MinuteMeditation
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: minute meditation
des:
Minute Meditation offers a short, guided meditation to help alleviate the stresses of human life. As opposed to other meditation skills, Minute Mediation is voiced in a soft Irish brogue as opposed to Alexa's normally harsh voice. 

Currently the skill only has one mediation, however, more will be added in the future.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
